					<span class="date_month">03</span>
					<span class="date_year">2008</span>
				</small>
				
				<div class="entry">
					<p>There is a big announcement today at Widemile and a new post by me.  However you won&#8217;t see it here.  Please head to <a href="http://testingblog.widemile.com" title="Billy's Blog">http://testingblog.widemile.com</a> to see the new site!  To celebrate Widemile&#8217;s annoucement, I have moved to a widemile.com domain and have a new design.</p>
<p>If you subscribe to my feedburner RSS feed, I have automatically changed it to the new site, however if you use the wordpress.com RSS feed, you will continue getting this site&#8217;s feed which is now dead.  Please update your feed to <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/billyblogwm" title="Billy's Blog RSS feed">http://feeds.feedburner.com/billyblogwm</a>.</p>
<p>I will no longer be updating this site, other than to point people to the new page.  <a href="http://testingblog.widemile.com" title="Billy's Blog">So please head there now!</a></p>
