				<small class="postmetadata">Categories : <a href="http://en.wordpress.com/tag/methodology/" title="View all posts in Methodology" rel="category tag">Methodology</a>, <a href="http://en.wordpress.com/tag/testing-concerns/" title="View all posts in Testing Concerns" rel="category tag">Testing Concerns</a>, <a href="http://widemile.wordpress.com/category/uncategorized/" title="View all posts in Uncategorized" rel="category tag">Uncategorized</a></small>			
			</div>
				
